<P>
   FILM-GOODING-PROFILE (Undated) _ Cuba Gooding Jr., who is famous
for his role in ``Jerry Mcguire,'' is picky when it comes to
choosing films.
</P>
<P>
   It may have cost him financially, but he's npw identified with
quality character parts. ``I think I'm on the track, sometimes in a
positive direction, sometimes in a negative. But on the whole I
think I'm sticking to my plan.'' And it seems to be paying off.
Gooding, 31, finally has his first real lead in a major studio film
with ``Instinct,'' which opens this weekend. By LOUIS PARKS
