   PAGE INCLUDES AT LEAST ONE COLOR ILLUSTRATION.
</P>
<P>
   BURTON CONTENDER: With his victory in the Coca-Cola 600 at
Charlotte last week, Jeff Burton proved that he's ready to contend
for the championship in 1999. He's second in points behind Dale
Jarrett.
</P>
<P>
   WITH: WINSTON CUP NOTES: Odds and ends column from Winston Cup.
</P>
<P>
   WITH: TRACK GRAPHIC: A 2-column color illustration of Dover
Downs International Speedway.
</P>
<P>
   WITH: WINSTON CUP STANDINGS
</P>
<P>
   WITH: BUSCH GRAND NATIONAL STANDINGS
</P>
