<P>
   LATIN POP: The astounding success of Puerto Rican pop singer
Ricky Martin, whose English-language debut CD sold 660,800 copies
in its first week of release, has cracked open a new frontier for
Latin pop and rock artists. (Includes 3-column B&AMP;W photo of the
