<P>
   CHINA-TRADE-ASSESS (Washington) _ News Analysis: The president
went through the annual ritual Thursday of renewing China's trade
status, but more interesting than the act _ there is little risk
China will be denied MFN _ was the rationale: There's no reason to
stop all progress with China just because human rights and security
has gone off the rails. By Elizabeth Sanger.
