   LOCKHEED-IMPACT _ ATLANTA _ The Lockheed of today isn't the
Lockheed of yesteryear, in terms of dominating the suburban economy
of northwest Atlanta. Still, the company is the largest single
employer and the prime source of jobs for a specific niche of
blue-collar worker. We talk to metro Atlanta economists, business
leaders to gauge the impact, and to the people down at the union
hall. (Visser/Farber, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
