   MASSACHUSETTS-AIRPORT-LOGAN. The nation's top aviation official
pledged to consider creating a regional airport network for New
England before deciding whether or not to recommend that Logan
International Airport build a new runway, two Massachusetts state
representatives said Wednesday. (500 words.) By Mark D. Preston
</P>
