the new movie ``Instinct,'' has reached a point in his career where
the ads trumpet ``Academy Award winner'' before his name. But the
ebullient actor had to overcome some difficult times to get to
where he is today. By ELVIS MITCHELL. Story will move in ``e''
entertainment category. &QL; 
