<HEADLINE>
THABO MBEKI, THE JOHN ADAMS OF SOUTH AFRICA 
</HEADLINE>
   (With SAFRICA-ELECTION)  
(DW) 
 By DONALD G. McNEIL Jr.   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service   
