<P>
   &QL; 
 &QL; 
MCCAINBIO (Washington) - A limp figure slowly descends from the
heavens with a parachute in tow. A mob of North Vietnamese people
await his landing. It appeared the folks piecing together Sen. John
McCain's presidential campaign video had uncovered spectacular
archival footage showing him falling to earth after his plane was
shot down on a bombing run over Hanoi during the Vietnam War. But
McCain's top aide said Thursday that the parachuting man depicted
in grainy black-and-white is not McCain at all, but rather stock
Defense Department footage of someone else. By JEFF BARKER. Story
will move in the ``A'' category. &QL; 
