<DOCNO> NYT19990603.0384 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> MISCELLANEOUS TEXT (slug-filter) </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-03 20:55 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2231 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-RAC-BELMONT-NOTES-LAD     06-03 0716
