<HEADLINE>
REFUGEES RECEIVE NEWS OF PEACE DEAL WITH MIXED EMOTIONS  
 
</HEADLINE>
   (This TIMELY 925-word ``separate buy'' article is from THE
INDEPENDENT newspaper in London.)  
  
 (EDITORS: We regret that this material is NOT available to clients
